1. Decide what kind of pizza we want
2. Decide how many pizzas we want
3. Decide how many beers we want
4. Call pizza place
  a. they answer - go to step 5
  b. they do not answer - retry step 4
5. Place the order
  a. Pay over phone - go to step 6
  b. Pay at door - go to step 7
6. Give credit card information
7. Wait for pizza
8. Answer the door
  a. Pay for pizza - skip if step 6 was used
9. Take pizza